   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give a Home to a Child in need from Cartagena</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">With your help we will protect 25 children who are in street life situations, they will be emotionally and physically rehabilitated to start a new life. We wish to continue providing services in the house of Dones, where we have changed many lives. The house has been adapted to accommodate our children; it includes a kitchen to prep freshly cooked meals, a spacious outside area to play, a psychology office, two comfortable bedrooms, four bathrooms, a living room, and classroom/computer room.</narrative>
  </description>
